9. Joining Windows Clients to the Domain

    Process:

	1. Set DNS to   DC01 IP
	2. Ping DC01
	3. System â†’ Rename â†’ Join Domain
	4. Enter domain credentials
	5. Restart
	6. Verify computer appears in  _Clients OU

Clients tested:

  Windows 10
  Windows 11 (TPM enabled in VirtualBox)


10. Backup & Restore

    Backup using Windows Server Backup

	Configured:

	*   Full Server Backup
	*   System State Backup
	*   Scheduled weekly backups

    Restore Tested

	* Restoring SYSVOL
	* Restoring AD DS DB


11. VirtualBox Networking Fixes

I solved:

	* VM stuck in Scaled Mode
	* DHCP conflicts with office network
	* Private NAT network creation
	* TPM 2.0 configuration for Windows 11
	* Expanding VDI disk (Virtual Media Manager â†’ Resize â†’ Diskmgmt.msc â†’ Extend 		Volume)


12. AD Health Monitoring

Commands used:

   powershell
	dcdiag /v
	repadmin /replsummary
	repadmin /showrepl
	Get-ADDomain
	Get-ADForest


All tests passed successfully.



13. Preparing AD for Azure Hybrid

	Steps done:

	* Created Azure AD tenant
	* Created resource groups
	* Downloaded Microsoft Entra Connect
	* Installed Entra Connect on DC01
	* Enabled Password Hash Sync
	* Selected OU Filtering
	* Synced users to Azure
	* Verified Sync Status using:

  * Synchronization Service Manager
  * Entra portal â†’ Connect Sync



